{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"seek"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"offset"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@goffset","text":"goffset"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"type","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@EA@GSeekType","text":"GSeekType"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","text":"CancellableRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"text":"? = nil) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Attempting to seek past the end of the stream will have different","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"results depending on if the stream is fixed-sized or resizable.  If","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the stream is resizable then seeking past the end and then writing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"will result in zeros filling the empty space.  Seeking past the end","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of a resizable stream and reading will result in EOF.  Seeking past"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the end of a fixed-sized stream will fail.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Any operation that would result in a negative offset will fail."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", then the operation can be cancelled by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancelled"},{"text":" will be returned.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Seeks in the stream by the given "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"offset"},{"type":"text","text":", modified by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"type"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileInputStream\/seek(offset:type:cancellable:)"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileInputStream","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileInputStream\/SeekableProtocol-Implementations"]]},"metadata":{"title":"seek(offset:type:cancellable:)","extendedModule":"GIO","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:3GIO16SeekableProtocolPAAE4seek6offset4type11cancellableSbs5Int64V_So9GSeekTypeaAA14CancellableRefVSgtKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO15FileInputStreamC","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"seek","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"offset","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:glibconfig.h@T@goffset","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"goffset"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"type"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GSeekType","preciseIdentifier":"c:@EA@GSeekType"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"kind":"text","text":":